#

Sweet Potato and Black Bean Bowl

40 min
$8
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick

Description

A wholesome bowl packed with sweet potatoes, black beans, and fresh toppings for a nutritious meal.

Ingredients

  • sweet potatoes: 2 medium
  • canned black beans: 1 can (15 oz)
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • avocado: 1
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup (chopped)
  • lime: 1 (juiced)
